      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a refined balance of performance and reliability. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure consistent mechanical integrity and long-term dependability. Featuring a well-preserved interior and a robust drivetrain, it represents an exceptional acquisition for the professional seeking a sophisticated driving experience without compromise. Secure this high-value asset today.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
